            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have always believed that confidence, hard work and perseverance are the keys to success. Delhi Public School, Gautam Buddh Nagar, Expressway is an epitome of success. A plethora of activities are organized for its students which help them turn into well rounded human beings. This School has a lot of academic potential and in addition helps develop social skills and builds character of its students leading to their holistic development . It is a wonderful place to work and I am happy to be associated with this School. The enriching ambience of the school encourage children to learn, explore, analyse and to come up with ingenious ideas, making learning joyful.",
